defs.name: TokenType
defs.value:
pub enum TokenType {
    NoToken,
    StreamStart(TEncoding),
    StreamEnd,

    /// major, minor
    VersionDirective(u32, u32),

    /// handle, prefix
    TagDirective(String, String),
    DocumentStart,
    DocumentEnd,
    BlockSequenceStart,
    BlockMappingStart,
    BlockEnd,
    FlowSequenceStart,
    FlowSequenceEnd,
    FlowMappingStart,
    FlowMappingEnd,
    BlockEntry,
    FlowEntry,
    Key,
    Value,
    Alias(String),
    Anchor(String),

    /// handle, suffix
    Tag(String, String),
    Scalar(TScalarStyle, String),
}
